  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973700/extras/381a3a6fd991e8bb5c70dd44b893d8be.webp?t=1726624425\" width=578 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973700/extras/7c270f7e2a36518a53d9ffec07a9d1de.avif?t=1726624425\" width=613 height=302 /></span><br><i><strong>Stories</strong></i><br>Four of the most popular figures in Lianhai City are trapped on top of a mysterious cruise ship at the same time!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973700/extras/3e76903226fef3db83a08f09b6ba1143.webp?t=1726624425\" width=29 height=18 /></span><br>The ship is actually the famous casino \"Lian Hai Casino\" which is disguised as a cruise ship.<br>It wanders the high seas and becomes a lawless trifle!<br><i><strong>Gameplay</strong></i><br>Players will choose one of four characters to play.<br>The hero is trapped on a cruise ship that is engaged in illegal gambling<br>In the game, players need to participate in the gambling games, communicate with the people on board, use their wisdom to escape the cruise ship, and discover the secrets of the cruise ship<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973700/extras/217c3a07e06c2434c7dff158888d4862.webp?t=1726624425\" width=600 height=46 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973700/extras/ce309a37e84e4fd246c5533cb89c56aa.avif?t=1726624425\" width=613 height=302 /></span><br><i><strong>Features</strong></i><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Multi-series game characters debut</li><li>Nostalgic-style graphics and music</li><li>Abundant characters and mini-games</li